# Testing discipline

- Test names describe behavior: `returns 404 when user does not exist`
- Unit tests for pure logic; integration tests at boundaries
- Mock external dependencies, not your own domain rules
- No merging with failing tests
- Run the narrowest test command for the changed files before claiming done

Bug fixes should include a regression test when practical.
